Play framework + Reactive MongoDB

Packages that are automatically imported<br/>
models._ (your models)<br/>
controllers._ (your controllers)<br/>
play.api.i18n._ (internationalization)<br/>
play.api.mvc._ (makes MVC components available)<br/>
play.api.data._ (tools for dealing with forms and validation)<br/>
views.%format%._ (if you are writing html, %format% is replaced by html)<br/><br/>

Working with strings: StringOps (scala.collection.immutable.StringOps)<br/>
user.name.capitalize
<br/><br/>